{"tid":1174940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本保齡球正妹竟40歲！「神級凍齡外表」一夜爆紅","createTime":"2019-05-28T08:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T09:06:45.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"794a7e42c18eebfa7255e2d57c896762c5314f97","tid":1174940,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"日本一名職業保齡球選手名和秋，成為媒體焦點，一頭黑色長髮加上濃眉大眼，很難想像眼前的她竟然已經40歲。日前她受邀參與節目，擔任堂本兄弟的保齡球老師，她的「凍齡外表」一夜圈粉，甚至一度登上運動員排行第一位。<br />\n<br />\n名和秋參與節目《KinKi Kidsのブンブブーン》，教導堂本兄弟打保齡球，當她一登場，堂本兄弟就大讚她與一般保齡球選手不同，多了年輕氣息，但一問之下才發現名和秋和他們一樣是1979年出生，且是個擁有16年職業保齡球資歷的的選手。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到播出後一夜之間，就俘虜日本全國男性而爆紅，她的個人部落格，更一度達到「Abema blog」運動員排行第一位。據了解，名和秋不但外表出色，更在2003年出道時就拿下，全日本選手權第四名，至今仍在保齡球界活躍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/28/1946384-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F28%2F1946384-XXL.jpg&h=a4b452ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/28/1946382-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F28%2F1946382-XXL.jpg&h=4b89f70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/28/1946383-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F28%2F1946383-XXL.jpg&h=d02cbb61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sutok0S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsutok0S.jpg&h=5c94fed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4HAb7y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4HAb7y.jpg&h=09845133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfC8w7y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfC8w7y.jpg&h=339a6db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HP7Ab7z.jpg\